Archive: Robert Croft leads Glamorgan celebration sing-song
Media playback is not supported on this deviceNew Glamorgan head coach Robert Croft knows what it is like for the Welsh county to enjoy success.In 1997 Croft led the celebrations after they won the County Championship by beating Somerset at Taunton.Croft has been appointed on a rolling contractas successor to Toby Radford, who left in December.